363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好阻樓主做中國人 一齊拉"},{"pid":"73a404e3e76fd4f196440653f9d203db8b7af7f8","tid":1799204,"uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係港獨派 係講獨派 唔好影衰我地爭取香港自治同獨立既本土派<br />\n<br />\n中共倒台/支爆/中國衰弱/有左真普選/有自治後/夠多外國聯手支持下/足夠&amp;幾乎絕對民意支持下亦充分發展左本土資源配套後就係時機 而家要做既係爭取左普選 加強自治權先 再慢慢宣傳教育解釋返個可行性<br />\n<br />\n連政治智慧 戰略需要 顧全大局 暗地推行 準備工夫做足再擺上台 等待時機配套成熟 都唔識 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得個有勇無謀 又唔知自己少數派 係都要騎劫 想越黎越少支持者 同藍屍一樣真係以為自己沉默大多數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港冇救了冇得獨立了 呢班冇腦有勇無謀嘅撚屌比人屌到化哂都死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840cdd2935e716aa903725250531988d7957158b","tid":1799204,"uid":56498,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ae286d593dcd362b86d614ccc4df26aea297ab7","tid":1799204,"uid":30506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4fa20b91f4113953ec95d3113db6e771f413451","tid":1799204,"uid":56498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfcab44d50536cf9e51b0b371bf2b62f352a6510","tid":1799204,"uid":7179,"like":3,"dislike"